          <text><![CDATA[<p>Adjusting Davis-Bacon for Inflation Act - Increases from $2,000 to $50,000 the contract threshold requiring the locally prevailing wage rate to be paid to various classes of laborers and mechanics working under federally-financed or federally-assisted contracts for construction, alteration, and repair of public buildings or public works (Davis-Bacon Act).</p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <updateDate>2013-04-18T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
